acter of  Lewis Carroll's  Alice's Adventures in Wonderland (  1865 ) and Through the Looking Glass (  1872 ), who was based on his child friend  Alice Liddell , daughter of the Dean of Christ Church, Oxford."],"variants":[{"name":"Alys","meanings":["Variant spelling of   Alice ."]},{"name":"Alis","meanings":["equivalent of <b>Alice</b> ."]}]}],"lifeSummary":"When Alice FitzReinfred was born in 1194, in Sussex, England, United Kingdom, her father, Joscelyn FritzReinfred, was 26 and her mother, Mrs. Joscelyn FritzReinfred, was 27. She had at least 2 sons and 1 daughter with Simon Echingham Sr.. She died in 1253, in England, United Kingdom, at the age of 59."},"et":{"1194–1253":"1194–1253","1185–1253":"1185–1253","1205–1269":"1205–1269","1218–1268":"1218–1268","1220–Female":"1220–Surnud","1168–Male":"1168–Surnud","1168–Female":"1168–Surnud","1205":"1205","1269":"1269","1268":"1268","1168":"1168","1220":"1220","1253":"1253","1185":"1185","1194":"1194","Abt 1218":"umbes 1218","1218":"1218","Etchingham, Sussex, England":"Etchingham, Sussex, Inglismaa, United Kingdom","Ticehurst, Sussex, England":"Ticehurst, Sussex, England","England":"Inglismaa, United Kingdom","Sussex, England":"Sussex, Inglismaa, United Kingdom"},"fi":{"1194–1253":"1194–1253","1185–1253":"1185–1253","1205–1269":"1205–1269","1218–1268":"1218–1268","1220–Female":"1220–Kuollut","1168–Male":"1168–Kuollut","1168–Female":"1168–Kuollut","1205":"1205","1269":"1269","1268":"1268","1168":"1168","1220":"1220","1253":"1253","1185":"1185","1194":"1194","Abt 1218":"noin 1218","1218":"1218","Etchingham, Sussex, England":"Etchingham, Sussex, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta","Ticehurst, Sussex, England":"Ticehurst, Sussex, England","England":"Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta","Sussex, England":"Sussex, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta"},"fr":{"1194–1253":"1194–1253","1185–1253":"1185–1253","1205–1269":"1205–1269","1218–1268":"1218–1268","1220–Female":"1220–Décédée","1168–Male":"1168–Décédé","1168–Female":"1168–D